metadata.name: Mermaid fisherwoman
metadata.description:
What can happen if a mermaid tries to catch a fish with a fishing rod? Maybe she 'll catch herself ) 
The buyer gets the right to personal non-commercial use of this image, and he will also receive from me this high-quality image in PNG format without a background for printing on T-shirts. 
You can see the process of creating this illustration on my YouTube channel
